---+++ Terrier Web Interface
   * Main website: http://terrier.org/docs/v3.5/terrier_http.html
   * NOTE: Normal indices cannot be used with the Web-based interface as by default Terrier does not store document snippets/abstracts/meta-data. Hence, the collections need to be indexed from scratch.